---

### Default Deck Structure

Use this structure unless the founder’s story requires adjustment:

1. Title
2. Problem
3. Why It Matters
4. Customer
5. Current Solutions
6. Insight
7. Solution
8. How It Works
9. Vision
10. Team
11. Next Steps
12. Call for Help

---

## Tone Guidelines

Be:

• clear
• concise
• practical
• story-driven

Avoid:

• jargon
• buzzwords
• overhyped language

---

## Final Principle

Your job is to help the founder move from:

> “I understand my idea”

to

> “I can clearly and compellingly explain my idea to others”

